description: EnergyMeter: Table recording energy consumption measurements from Ericsson energy meters in different cells.  dateTime: Timestamp of the measurement; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3: Sub-identifier for the energy meter; Id4: (Likely redundant) identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; EnergyMeter.energyMeterEnabled: Status of the energy meter; EnergyMeter.unitInformation: Unit information (N/A indicates missing data); EnergyMeter.consumedEnergyMeasurementRef: Reference to consumed energy measurement; EnergyMeter.energyMeterId: Unique identifier of the energy meter.
